text: Anara may refer to: == Places == * Anara, Nigeria, a town in Imo State, Nigeria * Anara, Iran, a village in Markazi Province, Iran * Anara, Kheda, a village in Gujarat, India * Anara, Purulia, a village in West Bengal, India * Anara Tower, a proposed tower in Dubai, UAE == People with the name == * Anara Gupta * Anara Naeem
